How to execute the DNN classifier in the singularity container:

1. export DNN_BASE=/path/to/the/module/basefolder

2. bash /path/to/singularity/envirnoment.sh /path/to/icetray/script.py [arguments]


Example:
bash /data/user/tglauch/DeepIceLearning/I3Module/examples/singularity_env.sh /data/user/tglauch/DeepIceLearning/I3Module/examples/example1.py --outfile /data/user/tglauch/test.npy --files /data/user/reimann/2017_07_25/diffuse_sample_for_ps/IC86_2012/processed/11029/11029_1.i3.bz2 --model mu_energy_reco_new

For running on a GPU start a condor job with avx support and CUDA availability (see gpu_job.sub for an example)

To run an interative job: condor_submit -interactive gpu_job.sub
